        {
            "id": 6142984,
            "title": "外資買超282億元 連4買挺台股戰史高 加碼兩檔記憶體股共9萬張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (5) 日大漲 314 點，終場收在最高點 24494 點，距離歷史高點 24570 僅差 76 點，蓄勢挑戰前高，外資也連四買，特別偏愛記憶體族群，大買華邦電、南亞科共 9 萬張，也青睞光學族群佳能 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2374:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2374\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2374-TW</a>) 跟華晶科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3059:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3059\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3059-TW</a>)，兩檔合計超過 2.7 萬張。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6142984/l/7cbd3fc16a636ddc11c47dd2eef4a7d9.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">台股蓄勢戰前高 外資敲進兩檔記憶體股 共加碼9萬張。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>三大法人今日合計買超 329.85 億元，外資買超 282.81 億元，連四買，自營商同步加碼 51.78 億元，連三買，投信賣超 4.73 億元，為連九賣；期貨方面，外資減碼空單 2199 口，未平倉空單口數降至 21304 口。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察外資動向，明顯偏愛債券 ETF 與記憶體族群，包括群益 ESG 投等債 20+(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00937B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00937B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00937B-TW</a>)、元大投資級公司債 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00720B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00720B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00720B-TW</a>)、元大美債 20 年 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00679B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00679B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00679B-TW</a>)，三檔合計達 18 萬張，同時敲進華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>) 與南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>) 共 9 萬張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資賣超則瞄準傳產股，中鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2002:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2002\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2002-TW</a>)、華新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1605-TW</a>)、富喬 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1815:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1815\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1815-TW</a>)、台玻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1802:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1802\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1802-TW</a>) 全數入列賣超前五名，張數都在 1 萬張以上，其他如凱基金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2883:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2883\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2883-TW</a>)、漢翔 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2634:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2634\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2634-TW</a>)、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)、鴻準 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2354:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2354\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2354-TW</a>) 也都有 7 千至 1.5 萬張的水準。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>投信與自營商也與外資有志一同，雙雙調節台玻，兩者合計賣超逾 2 千張，也同步加碼京元電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2449:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2449\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2449-TW</a>)，一共敲進超過 3 千張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6142984",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-05 19:18:35",
